{"id":4068,"date":"2025-06-12T17:23:46","date_gmt":"2025-06-12T10:23:46","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/?p=4068"},"modified":"2025-06-12T17:23:46","modified_gmt":"2025-06-12T10:23:46","slug":"dau-tay-trang-han-quoc","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/thong-tin-nganh\/dau-tay-trang-han-quoc\/","title":{"rendered":"Top 5 d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang h\u00e0n qu\u1ed1c ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><b><i>D\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<\/i><\/b><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng t\u00edn \u0111\u1ed3 skincare. Nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u m\u00e0 v\u1eabn d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da. V\u1edbi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh. C\u00e1c d\u00f2ng d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang t\u1eeb x\u1ee9 s\u1edf kim chi kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, c\u1eb7n trang \u0111i\u1ec3m. M\u00e0 c\u00f2n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y. V\u1eady \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u00e1ng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m nh\u1ea5t. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 ngay top d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay!<\/span><\/i><\/p>\n\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"dau-tay-trang-han-quoc-co-thuc-su-tot\"><\/span><b>D\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t?\u00a0<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<\/span><\/i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh. M\u00e0 c\u00f2n ghi \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u m\u00e0 v\u1eabn d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9 tr\u00ean da. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 l\u1edbp trang \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 v\u1edbi l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m nh\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4069\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4069\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4069\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-1.webp\" alt=\"D\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-1.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-1-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-1-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-1-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4069\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><\/em> <em>D\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u1ed1t<\/em><\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da d\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n. L\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn <\/span><b>d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang cho da d\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> t\u1eeb H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn. Gi\u1ea3m nguy c\u01a1 b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng m\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean cho da. S\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng v\u1ec1 gi\u00e1 c\u1ea3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ed9ng l\u1edbn. Gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u1edd nh\u1eefng \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i n\u00e0y, d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0 \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn y\u00eau th\u00edch c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u t\u00edn \u0111\u1ed3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p tr\u00ean to\u00e0n c\u1ea7u.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"cach-chon-dau-tay-trang-han-quoc-phu-hop-cho-tung-loai-da\"><\/span><b>C\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho t\u1eebng lo\u1ea1i da<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 t\u00ecm m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch. M\u00e0 c\u00f2n c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi lo\u1ea1i da v\u00e0 nhu c\u1ea7u ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ti\u00eau ch\u00ed quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4070\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4070\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4070\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-2.webp\" alt=\"C\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-2.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-2-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-2-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-2-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4070\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">C\u00e1ch ch\u1ecdn d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"thanh-phan-an-toan-lanh-tinh\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n an to\u00e0n, l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n trong d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch. Kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng. Khi ch\u1ecdn d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, h\u00e3y \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u00e1c chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. Nh\u01b0 d\u1ea7u hoa tr\u00e0, d\u1ea7u jojoba, d\u1ea7u h\u1ea1t nho ho\u1eb7c d\u1ea7u qu\u1ea3 m\u01a1. Nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0y gi\u00fap h\u00f2a tan b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, c\u1eb7n trang \u0111i\u1ec3m. M\u00e0 v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho l\u00e0n da.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da d\u1ec5 n\u1ed5i m\u1ee5n, h\u00e3y t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9a tinh d\u1ea7u tr\u00e0m tr\u00e0. Ho\u1eb7c salicylic acid \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang cho da d\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 sung c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n kh\u00e1ng vi\u00eam. Gi\u00fap gi\u1ea3m thi\u1ec3u nguy c\u01a1 b\u00edt t\u1eafc l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"ket-cau-dau-tay-trang-%e2%80%93-long-hay-dac-moi-tot\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u1ebft c\u1ea5u d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang \u2013 L\u1ecfng hay \u0111\u1eb7c m\u1edbi t\u1ed1t?<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed7i lo\u1ea1i da s\u1ebd ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang kh\u00e1c nhau. N\u1ebfu s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u00e0n da kh\u00f4, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ecdn d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c c\u00f3 k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u \u0111\u1eb7c. Gi\u00e0u d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m v\u00e0 b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 l\u1edbp m\u00e0ng \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang cho da d\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n n\u00ean c\u00f3 k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u l\u1ecfng, d\u1ec5 nh\u0169 h\u00f3a. Gi\u00fap h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u h\u01a1n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y b\u00edt t\u1eafc.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"chon-dung-loai-dau-tay-trang-theo-tinh-trang-da\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang lo\u1ea1i d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang theo t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh lo\u1ea1i da l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p. N\u1ebfu da b\u1ea1n thu\u1ed9c nh\u00f3m nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m. H\u00e3y \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n, h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u ho\u1eb7c d\u1ea7u kho\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh k\u00edch \u1ee9ng. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ai c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da d\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n, vi\u1ec7c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang cho da d\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n. V\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00e3 nh\u1eddn v\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng da r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi mua, h\u00e3y nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u k\u1ef9 s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u. \u0110\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, an to\u00e0n v\u00e0 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi nhu c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/span><\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"top-5-dau-tay-trang-han-quoc-duoc-yeu-thich-nhat-hien-nay\"><\/span><b>Top 5 d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch nh\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nay<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m <\/span><b>d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> lu\u00f4n n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch y\u00eau th\u00edch c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng t\u00edn \u0111\u1ed3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1edd kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u. Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 ti\u00ean ti\u1ebfn. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 lo\u1ea1i <\/span><b>d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang cho da d\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n<\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"> v\u00e0 m\u1ecdi lo\u1ea1i da \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"gsc-natural-makeup-remove-%e2%80%93-dau-tay-trang-diu-nhe-lam-sach-sau\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">GSC Natural Makeup Remove \u2013 D\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang d\u1ecbu nh\u1eb9, l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m v\u1eeba l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u1eeba gi\u1eef \u1ea9m t\u1ed1t. D\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eeb GSC l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua. V\u1edbi c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c gi\u00e0u d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t t\u1eeb c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i d\u1ea7u th\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0: Macadamia, Jojoba v\u00e0 Olive. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n, d\u1ea7u th\u1eeba v\u00e0 l\u1edbp trang \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 da.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4071\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4071\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4071\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-3.webp\" alt=\"GSC Natural Makeup Remove\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-3.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-3-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-3-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-3-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4071\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">GSC Natural Makeup Remove<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Tinh d\u1ea7u Macadamia, Jojoba v\u00e0 Olive: L\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch s\u00e2u, gi\u00fap da m\u1ecbn m\u00e0ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Isopropyl Myristate: H\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 nh\u0169 h\u00f3a nhanh, gi\u00fap da th\u00f4ng tho\u00e1ng sau khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean: K\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1eeb d\u1ea7u h\u1ea1t Macca, d\u1ea7u Oliu, b\u01a1 h\u1ea1t m\u1ee1 gi\u00fap nu\u00f4i d\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u00e0n da kh\u1ecfe m\u1ea1nh. V\u1edbi th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n an to\u00e0n l\u00e0nh t\u00ednh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3 m\u1eaft v\u00e0 m\u00f4i<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"-innisfree-apple-seed-cleansing-oil\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u00a0Innisfree Apple Seed Cleansing Oil<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">L\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u m\u1ef9 ph\u1ea9m thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Innisfree mang \u0111\u1ebfn d\u00f2ng d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c v\u1edbi chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb h\u1ea1t t\u00e1o, gi\u00fap l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4072\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4072\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4072\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-4.webp\" alt=\"\u00a0Innisfree Apple Seed Cleansing Oil\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-4.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-4-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-4-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-4-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4072\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Innisfree Apple Seed Cleansing Oil<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u00e1o t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean gi\u00fap lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf l\u1edbp trang \u0111i\u1ec3m, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m kh\u00f4 da.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c an to\u00e0n, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed9c h\u1ea1i.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u00f9i h\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u00e1o t\u01b0\u01a1i m\u00e1t, t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"skin1004-madagascar-centella-light-cleansing-oil\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Skin1004 Madagascar Centella Light Cleansing Oil\u00a0<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u00e0nh ri\u00eang cho nh\u1eefng ai c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m ho\u1eb7c d\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n. S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0y ch\u1ee9a chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t rau m\u00e1 t\u1eeb Madagascar, gi\u00fap l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu v\u00e0 c\u1ea5p \u1ea9m m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4073\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4073\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4073\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-5.webp\" alt=\"Skin1004 Madagascar Centella Light Cleansing Oil\u00a0\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-5.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-5-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-5-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-5-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4073\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Skin1004 Madagascar Centella Light Cleansing Oil<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u00a0Th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t rau m\u00e1 Madagascar: Gi\u00fap l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da, gi\u1ea3m s\u01b0ng vi\u00eam do m\u1ee5n.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i d\u1ea7u th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt: Cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m, h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf kh\u00f4 da sau khi t\u1ea9y trang.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Nh\u0169 h\u00f3a nhanh, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang cho da d\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n, gi\u00fap l\u1ed7 ch\u00e2n l\u00f4ng s\u1ea1ch tho\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"klairs-gentle-black-fresh-cleansing-oil\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Klairs Gentle Black Fresh Cleansing Oil<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Klairs n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9a c\u1ed3n, paraben hay h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u nh\u00e2n t\u1ea1o. Gi\u00fap t\u1ed1i \u01b0u h\u00f3a quy tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y k\u00edch \u1ee9ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4074\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4074\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4074\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-6.webp\" alt=\"Klairs Gentle Black Fresh Cleansing Oil\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-6.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-6-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-6-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-6-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4074\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Klairs Gentle Black Fresh Cleansing Oil<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0110i\u1ec3m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ch\u1ee9a 85% d\u1ea7u th\u1ef1c v\u1eadt t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean, an to\u00e0n cho l\u00e0n da nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">D\u1ea7u h\u1ea1t l\u00fd chua \u0111en: Gi\u00e0u ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ed1ng oxy h\u00f3a, b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 da kh\u1ecfi t\u00e1c nh\u00e2n m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">K\u1ebft c\u1ea5u nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng, d\u1ec5 nh\u0169 h\u00f3a, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang cho da d\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n v\u00e0 da h\u1ed7n h\u1ee3p.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"the-face-shop-rice-water-bright-rich-cleansing-oil\"><\/span><i><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">The Face Shop Rice Water Bright Rich Cleansing Oil<\/span><\/i><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c y\u00eau th\u00edch nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb The Face Shop. D\u00f2ng d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch da. M\u00e0 c\u00f2n gi\u00fap d\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1eafng nh\u1edd chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc g\u1ea1o.<\/span><\/p>\n<figure id=\"attachment_4075\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-4075\" style=\"width: 800px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-4075\" src=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-7.webp\" alt=\"The Face Shop Rice Water Bright Rich Cleansing Oil\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-7.webp 800w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-7-300x169.webp 300w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-7-768x432.webp 768w, https:\/\/gsccos.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/06\/43-7-600x338.webp 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-4075\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The Face Shop Rice Water Bright Rich Cleansing Oil<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc g\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ea7u c\u00e1m g\u1ea1o: L\u00e0m s\u00e1ng da, cung c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea9m t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Vitamin E: Gi\u00fap da m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i, gi\u1ea3m t\u00e1c h\u1ea1i t\u1eeb m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c gi\u00e0u d\u01b0\u1ee1ng ch\u1ea5t, ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p cho da kh\u00f4 v\u00e0 nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m.<\/span><span style=\"font-weight: 400\"><br \/>\n<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong-ket\"><\/span><b>T\u1ed5ng k\u1ebft<\/b><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">M\u1ed7i lo\u1ea1i <\/span><b>d\u1ea7u t\u1ea9y trang H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c <\/b><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">\u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00f4ng d\u1ee5ng ri\u00eang bi\u1ec7t. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 l\u00e0n da d\u1ea7u m\u1ee5n, h\u00e3y \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u00e1c s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh ph\u1ea7n ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t d\u1ea7u. V\u00e0 l\u00e0m d\u1ecbu da nh\u01b0 rau m\u00e1 ho\u1eb7c tr\u00e0m tr\u00e0.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu da kh\u00f4 ho\u1eb7c nh\u1ea1y c\u1ea3m, h\u00e3y ch\u1ecdn s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m c\u00f3 chi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u1ea9m nh\u01b0 d\u1ea7u h\u1ea1t Macca ho\u1eb7c n\u01b0\u1edbc g\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec l\u00e0n da m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i. B\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eed qua s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m n\u00e0o trong danh s\u00e1ch tr\u00ean ch\u01b0a? Chia s\u1ebb ngay tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n nh\u00e9!\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>